OL,7,FA motorcycle trader has been convicted
OL,8,Fof causing the deaths of two
OL,9,Fpedestrians by careless driving after
OL,10,Fthey were run over by his van while
OL,11,Fcrossing a road in Carlisle.
OL,13,FTerry Abson, 62, died at the scene
OL,14,Fwhich occurred on the city's West
OL,15,FTower Street just before 1pm on March
OL,16,F1 2021. His partner, Gina Lands, 56,
OL,17,Fpassed away in hospital seven days
OL,18,Flater.
