OL,7,FMarc Large, 49, went on trial at this
OL,8,Fweek. He denied two charges of causing
OL,9,Fthe deaths of Mr Abson and Miss Lands
OL,10,Fby careless driving.
OL,12,FJurors heard at the time he was on a
OL,13,Fphone call ` in a vehicle fitted with
OL,14,Fa hands-free system ` which ended four
OL,15,Fseconds after the fatal collision.
