OL,7,FLarge did not give evidence during his
OL,8,Ftrial. He had provided a prepared
OL,9,Fstatement when interviewed, saying
OL,10,Fthat his visual field was affected by
OL,11,Fglaring sun and recalling that he
OL,12,Fcarried out emergency stop braking. He
OL,13,Fdenied being distracted and had
OL,14,Fstated: "I really can't explain how
OL,15,Fthis collision occurred as I never saw
OL,16,Fthe couple until a split second before
OL,17,FI hit them."
