OL,7,FA police collision investigator had
OL,8,Fconcluded sunlight would not have
OL,9,Faffected Large's ability to see
OL,10,Fpedestrians. The officer had not found
OL,11,Fany skid marks on the carriageway
OL,12,Fsurface and said the couple were on
OL,13,Fthe road for about five seconds.
OL,15,FCCTV showed traffic lights for
