OL,7,FOpening the case, prosecutor Tim Evans
OL,8,Fhad said of Large: "The Crown say he
OL,9,Fhad ample time and opportunity to pay
OL,10,Fattention to what was on the road
OL,11,Fahead of him, and he ought to have
OL,12,Fseen that the two deceased were
OL,13,Falready on the road as he was
OL,14,Fapproaching the lights."
OL,16,FOn Friday jurors found Large guilty of
OL,17,Fcausing the deaths of Mr Abson and
OL,18,FMiss Lands by careless driving after
OL,19,Fhearing all evidence in the trial.
