OL,7,FThe case was adjourned by Judge
OL,8,FMichael Fanning. Large is due to be
OL,9,Fsentenced at the crown court on March
OL,10,F22, and in the meantime he has been
OL,11,Fbailed and handed an interim driving
OL,12,Fban.
OL,14,FIn a tribute to Mr Abson and Miss
OL,15,FLands which was issued through police
OL,16,Fafter the tragedy, relatives described
OL,17,Fthe couple as caring parents and told
OL,18,Fhow they "take comfort that they are
OL,19,Fnow together again as they were in
OL,20,Flife".
